        <infon key="n">1</infon>
        <offset>0</offset>
        <text>Resistance and resilience of benthic biofilm communities from a temperate saltmarsh to desiccation and rewetting
</text>
      </sentence>
    </passage>
    <passage>
      <offset>113</offset>
      <infon key="type">body</infon>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>113</offset>
        <text>Periods of desiccation and rewetting are regular, yet stressful events encountered by saltmarsh microbial communities.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>232</offset>
        <text>To examine the resistance and resilience of microbial biofilms to such stresses, sediments from saltmarsh creeks were allowed to desiccate for 23 days, followed by rewetting for 4 days, whereas control sediments were maintained under a natural tidal cycle.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>489</offset>
        <text>In the top 2 mm of the dry sediments, salinity increased steadily from 36 to 231 over 23 days, and returned to seawater salinity on rewetting.
</text>
        <annotation id="T1">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T1</infon>
          <location length="9" offset="536"/>
          <text>increased</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T2">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T2</infon>
          <location length="8" offset="527"/>
          <text>salinity</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E1">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">E1</infon>
          <node refid="T1" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T2" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>632</offset>
        <text>After 3 days, desiccated sediments had a lower chlorophyll a (Chl a) fluorescence signal as benthic diatoms ceased to migrate to the surface, with a recovery in cell migration and Chl a fluorescence on rewetting.
</text>
        <annotation id="T3">
          <infon key="type">Decrease</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T3</infon>
          <location length="5" offset="673"/>
          <text>lower</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T4">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T4</infon>
          <location length="41" offset="679"/>
          <text>chlorophyll a (Chl a) fluorescence signal</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T7">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T7</infon>
          <location length="30" offset="845"/>
          <text>Extracellular beta-glucosidase</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E2">
          <infon key="type">Decrease</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">E2</infon>
          <node refid="T3" role="Decrease"/>
          <node refid="T4" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>845</offset>
        <text>Extracellular beta-glucosidase and aminopeptidase activities decreased within the first week of drying, but increased sharply on rewetting.
</text>
        <annotation id="T5">
          <infon key="type">Decrease</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T5</infon>
          <location length="9" offset="906"/>
          <text>decreased</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T6">
          <infon key="type">And</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T6</infon>
          <location length="3" offset="876"/>
          <text>and</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T8">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T8</infon>
          <location length="25" offset="880"/>
          <text>aminopeptidase activities</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T9">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T9</infon>
